verses.verse: This is the <S%H1293>blessing,<s%> with which <S%H4872>Moses<s%> the <S%H376>man<s%> of <S%H430>God<s%> <S%H1288>blessed<s%> the <S%H1121>children<s%> of <S%H3478>Israel<s%> <S%H6440>before<s%> his <S%H4194>death.<s%>

He <S%H559>said,<s%> <S%H3068>"Yahweh<s%> <S%H935>came<s%> from <S%H5514>Sinai,<s%> And <S%H2224>rose<s%> from <S%H8165>Seir<s%> to <S%H3313>them.<s%> He shone forth from <S%H2022>Mount<s%> <S%H6290>Paran.<s%> He <S%H857>came<s%> from the ten <S%H7233>thousands<s%> of holy <S%H6944>ones.<s%> At his right <S%H3225>hand<s%> was a <S%H799>fiery<s%> law for <S%H1881>them.<s%>

<S%H637>Yes,<s%> he <S%H2245>loves<s%> the <S%H5971>people.<s%> All his <S%H6918>saints<s%> are in your <S%H3027>hand.<s%> They sat <S%H8497>down<s%> at your <S%H7272>feet;<s%> each <S%H5375>receives<s%> your <S%H1703>words.<s%>
<S%H4872>Moses<s%> <S%H6680>commanded<s%> us a <S%H8451>law,<s%> An <S%H4181>inheritance<s%> for the <S%H6952>assembly<s%> of <S%H3290>Jacob.<s%>

He was <S%H4428>king<s%> in <S%H3484>Jeshurun,<s%> When the <S%H7218>heads<s%> of the <S%H5971>people<s%> were <S%H622>gathered,<s%> All the <S%H7626>tribes<s%> of <S%H3478>Israel<s%> <S%H3162>together.<s%>
"Let <S%H7205>Reuben<s%> <S%H2421>live,<s%> and not <S%H4191>die;<s%> Nor let his <S%H4962>men<s%> be <S%H4557>few.<s%>"

This is for <S%H3063>Judah.<s%> He <S%H559>said,<s%> <S%H8085>"Hear,<s%> <S%H3068>Yahweh,<s%> the <S%H6963>voice<s%> of <S%H3063>Judah.<s%> <S%H935>Bring<s%> him in to his <S%H5971>people.<s%> With his <S%H3027>hands<s%> he <S%H7227>contended<s%> for <S%H5828>himself.<s%> You shall be a help against his <S%H6862>adversaries.<s%>"

Of <S%H3878>Levi<s%> he <S%H559>said,<s%> "Your <S%H8550>Thummim<s%> and your <S%H224>Urim<s%> are with your <S%H2623>godly<s%> <S%H376>one,<s%> whom you <S%H5254>proved<s%> at <S%H4532>Massah,<s%> with whom you <S%H7378>strove<s%> at the <S%H4325>waters<s%> of <S%H4809>Meribah;<s%>

who <S%H559>said<s%> of his <S%H1>father,<s%> and of his <S%H517>mother,<s%> <S%H7200><s%> 'I have not seen <S%H5234>him;<s%>' Neither did he acknowledge his <S%H251>brothers,<s%> Nor did he <S%H3045>know<s%> his own <S%H1121>children:<s%> For they have <S%H8104>observed<s%> your <S%H565>word,<s%> and <S%H5341>keep<s%> your <S%H1285>covenant.<s%>

They shall <S%H3384>teach<s%> <S%H3290>Jacob<s%> your <S%H4941>ordinances,<s%> and <S%H3478>Israel<s%> your <S%H8451>law.<s%> They shall <S%H7760>put<s%> <S%H6988>incense<s%> <S%H639>before<s%> <S%H3632>you,<s%> and whole burnt offering on your <S%H4196>altar.<s%>

<S%H3068>Yahweh,<s%> <S%H1288>bless<s%> his <S%H2428>substance.<s%> <S%H7521>Accept<s%> the <S%H6467>work<s%> of his <S%H3027>hands.<s%> <S%H4272>Strike<s%> through the <S%H4975>hips<s%> of those who <S%H6965>rise<s%> up against <S%H8130>him,<s%> of those who hate <S%H4480>him,<s%> that they not <S%H6965>rise<s%> <S%H6965>again.<s%>"

Of <S%H1144>Benjamin<s%> he <S%H559>said,<s%> "The <S%H3039>beloved<s%> of <S%H3068>Yahweh<s%> shall <S%H7931>dwell<s%> in <S%H983>safety<s%> by <S%H2653>him.<s%> He covers him all the <S%H3117>day<s%> <S%H7931>long.<s%> He dwells between his <S%H3802>shoulders.<s%>"

Of <S%H3130>Joseph<s%> he <S%H559>said,<s%> "His <S%H776>land<s%> is <S%H1288>blessed<s%> by <S%H3068>Yahweh,<s%> for the precious <S%H4022>things<s%> of the <S%H8064>heavens,<s%> for the <S%H2919>dew,<s%> for the <S%H8415>deep<s%> that couches <S%H7257>beneath,<s%>
for the <S%H4022>precious<s%> things of the <S%H8393>fruits<s%> of the <S%H8121>sun,<s%> for the precious <S%H4022>things<s%> of the <S%H1645>growth<s%> of the <S%H3391>moons,<s%>
for the chief <S%H7218>things<s%> of the <S%H6924>ancient<s%> <S%H2042>mountains,<s%> for the precious <S%H4022>things<s%> of the <S%H5769>everlasting<s%> <S%H1389>hills,<s%>

for the precious <S%H4022>things<s%> of the <S%H776>earth<s%> and its <S%H4393>fullness,<s%> the good <S%H7522>will<s%> of him who <S%H7931>lived<s%> in the <S%H5572>bush.<s%> Let this <S%H935>come<s%> on the <S%H7218>head<s%> of <S%H3130>Joseph,<s%> on the crown of the <S%H6936>head<s%> of him who was <S%H5139>separate<s%> from his <S%H251>brothers.<s%>

The <S%H1060>firstborn<s%> of his <S%H7794>herd,<s%> <S%H1926>majesty<s%> is <S%H7161>his.<s%> His horns are the <S%H7161>horns<s%> of the wild <S%H7214>ox.<s%> With them he shall <S%H5055>push<s%> <S%H3162>all<s%> of the <S%H5971>peoples,<s%> to the <S%H657>ends<s%> of the <S%H776>earth:<s%> They are the ten <S%H7233>thousands<s%> of <S%H669>Ephraim.<s%> They are the <S%H505>thousands<s%> of <S%H4519>Manasseh.<s%>"
Of <S%H2074>Zebulun<s%> he <S%H559>said,<s%> <S%H8055>"Rejoice,<s%> <S%H2074>Zebulun,<s%> in your going <S%H3318>out;<s%> and <S%H3485>Issachar,<s%> in your <S%H168>tents.<s%>

They shall <S%H7121>call<s%> the <S%H5971>peoples<s%> to the <S%H2022>mountain.<s%> There they will <S%H2076>offer<s%> <S%H2077>sacrifices<s%> of <S%H6664>righteousness,<s%> for they shall <S%H3243>draw<s%> out the <S%H8228>abundance<s%> of the <S%H3220>seas,<s%> the <S%H2934>hidden<s%> <S%H8226>treasures<s%> of the <S%H2344>sand.<s%>"

Of <S%H1410>Gad<s%> he <S%H559>said,<s%> "He who <S%H7337>enlarges<s%> <S%H1410>Gad<s%> is <S%H1288>blessed.<s%> He <S%H7931>dwells<s%> as a <S%H3833>lioness,<s%> and <S%H2963>tears<s%> the <S%H2220>arm,<s%> <S%H637>yes,<s%> the crown of the <S%H6936>head.<s%>

He <S%H7200>provided<s%> the first <S%H7225>part<s%> for <S%H2710>himself,<s%> for there was the lawgiver's <S%H2513>portion<s%> <S%H5603>reserved.<s%> He <S%H857>came<s%> with the <S%H7218>heads<s%> of the <S%H5971>people.<s%> He <S%H6213>executed<s%> the <S%H6666>righteousness<s%> of <S%H3068>Yahweh,<s%> His <S%H4941>ordinances<s%> with <S%H3478>Israel.<s%>"
Of <S%H1835>Dan<s%> he <S%H559>said,<s%> <S%H1835>"Dan<s%> is a <S%H738>lion<s%>'s <S%H1482>cub<s%> that <S%H2187>leaps<s%> out of <S%H1316>Bashan.<s%>"

Of <S%H5321>Naphtali<s%> he <S%H559>said,<s%> <S%H5321>"Naphtali,<s%> <S%H7649>satisfied<s%> with <S%H7522>favor,<s%> <S%H4392>full<s%> of the <S%H1293>blessing<s%> of <S%H3068>Yahweh,<s%> <S%H3423>Possess<s%> the <S%H3220>west<s%> and the <S%H1864>south.<s%>"

Of <S%H836>Asher<s%> he <S%H559>said,<s%> <S%H836>"Asher<s%> is <S%H1288>blessed<s%> with <S%H1121>children.<s%> Let him be <S%H7521>acceptable<s%> to his <S%H251>brothers.<s%> Let him <S%H2881>dip<s%> his <S%H7272>foot<s%> in <S%H8081>oil.<s%>
Your <S%H4515>bars<s%> shall be <S%H1270>iron<s%> and <S%H5178>brass.<s%> As your <S%H3117>days,<s%> so your strength will <S%H1679>be.<s%>
"There is none like <S%H410>God,<s%> <S%H3484>Jeshurun,<s%> who <S%H7392>rides<s%> on the <S%H8064>heavens<s%> for your <S%H5828>help,<s%> In his <S%H1346>excellency<s%> on the <S%H7834>skies.<s%>

The <S%H6924>eternal<s%> <S%H430>God<s%> is your <S%H4585>dwelling<s%> <S%H5769>place.<s%> Underneath are the everlasting <S%H2220>arms.<s%> He thrust <S%H1644>out<s%> the <S%H341>enemy<s%> from <S%H6440>before<s%> <S%H559>you,<s%> and said, <S%H8045><s%> 'Destroy!'

<S%H3478>Israel<s%> <S%H7931>dwells<s%> in <S%H983>safety;<s%> the <S%H5869>fountain<s%> of <S%H3290>Jacob<s%> <S%H910>alone,<s%> In a <S%H776>land<s%> of <S%H1715>grain<s%> and new <S%H8492>wine.<s%> <S%H8064>Yes,<s%> his heavens drop <S%H6201>down<s%> <S%H2919>dew.<s%>

You are <S%H835>happy,<s%> <S%H3478>Israel.<s%> Who is like <S%H5971>you,<s%> a people <S%H3467>saved<s%> by <S%H3068>Yahweh,<s%> the <S%H4043>shield<s%> of your <S%H5828>help,<s%> the <S%H2719>sword<s%> of your <S%H1346>excellency!<s%> Your <S%H341>enemies<s%> shall <S%H3584>submit<s%> themselves to <S%H1869>you.<s%> You shall tread on their high <S%H1116>places.<s%>"
